{"title":"海外诗简","authors":["辛笛"],"dates":[{"year":1982,"month":2,"day":11}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"海外诗简"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"辛笛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风景画片"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飞过蓝天大海落"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"脚在千水的湖边"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山鸟和海鸥来来去去"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亲切忘掉了语言"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走进明丽的山川"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一心却去拣风景画片"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"寄去时间和地点"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伴着对祖国深情的思念"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“代沟”上握手"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"过午的阳光照亮林荫"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"灰鸽白鸽跳跃在绿色草坪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我边在诗叶上题字"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"边听你絮语低声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我忘记了你是我学生的女儿"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你忘记了我祖父般的年龄"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你谈论你青春的梦想"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我心上响起驼铃"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"隔代人共同来找生命的支点"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鸿沟能不能就美好地犁平？"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}